skins.shipDescription: King George V-class battleship ¨C King George V.
skins.selfIntroduction: The nameship of the King George V-class battleships is none other than me. I served as flagship for my country, leading the fleet into numerous battles including the fateful encounter with Bismarck. After getting a brief taste of that thrill, I have been craving to cross swords with her once again... But I digress - is there anything else you'd like to know about me?
skins.acquisition: So this is my new battlefield. Ahh, how I've long awaited this... By the way, are you my commander? You are in the presence of King George V ¨C do use me well.
skins.login: Commander, did you already partake of supper?
skins.details: My standing within the Royal Family? Hmm... If I had to draw a comparison, I'd say "Knight Commander" would be the most fitting... Hahaha...
skins.secretaryIdle1: Commander, this fleet only functions because of you. Don't get sloppy on us.
skins.secretaryIdle2: Wales and Yorkie? It's a bit of a shame that they don't act more like cute little sisters, but I am glad that they have strong personalities.
skins.secretaryIdle3: In my eyes, there is no leader in this world more worthy of my loyalty than Her Majesty, Queen Elizabeth. Does that make sense to you, Commander?
skins.secretaryIdle4: The Royals' cuisine is all bland? Hogwash. That's just an unfortunate stereotype.
skins.secretaryTouch: Why do I have a mountain of snacks before me? Isn't it obvious? One cannot move on an empty stomach.
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Ohh? I wasn't aware that you possessed such audacity, Commander.

skins.shipDescription: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander... I don't get to wear a dress very often, so it took me a bit longer. Let's get going, then. Remember, you'll be the lead tonight. Haha~
